            BROADCAST-GATEWAY • v2.1
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <style>{`
        #container-92100ea7c1b81dec5e887cbf56a2c891 { width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: center; padding: 10px; }
      `}</style>
